  #1  Save state lost on scroll — UX regression
  #2  Like state lost on refresh — UX regression

HIGH (visible UX issues or security):
  #9  Load-more threshold too late
  #13 Dangling pending posts
  #15 SuperAdmin key in sessionStorage
  #16 No cache TTL (stale data)
  #12 IntersectionObserver re-register issue

